data.description:
Brick Home In Alexander Crossing Subdivision With Open Floorplan, 4 Bedrooms & 2 Baths.
Features Include:   *Laminate & Tile Floors In Downstairs & Carpeting In Upstairs  *Kitchen Offers A  Large Breakfast Bar, New Pendant Lighting & Updated Tiled Backsplash  *Great Room Offers Soaring Ceiling, Corner Fireplace With Gas Logs & French Door To Patio  *Primary Bedroom Overlooks The Backyard, Vaulted Ceiling & Luxury Bath With Updated Light Fixture, Corner Jetted Tub & Separate Shower  *Two Guest Bedrooms Share The Updated 2nd Bath   *Upstairs Bonus Room/4th Bedroom Offers A Closet & Attic Access   *Attic Has Lots Of Storage Space.     Wood Privacy Fenced Backyard With Gate Which Opens To Neighborhood Green Space.   2 Car Garage.  

Approximate Room Sizes:
Great Room 19 x 14
Kitchen 10 x 8
Dining Room  11 x 9
Primary Bedroom 15 x 13
Guest Bedroom #1    10 x 11
Guest Bedroom #2    10 x 11
Bonus/Guest Bedroom #3   15 x 11
